{"tid":1835724,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵：即時停售所有往來武漢高鐵車票","createTime":"2020-01-23T02:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T02:58:05.000Z","uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6908af3172afad05cc474a59402737ab946b3fd8","tid":1835724,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504368-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504368-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=497792a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504368-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=15c1b007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504368-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，經與內地鐵路單位溝通後，即時停售所有往來武漢的高鐵車票。往來武漢的列車服務目前仍然維持正常，港鐵正與內地相關單位保持緊密溝通，有最新消息會盡快通知乘客，已購票的乘客如欲退票，可獲全數退款。"},{"pid":"12d34412246ba088ca33d1491e152246bc89acbb","tid":1835724,"uid":32934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"TOO LATE"},{"pid":"68016a0b88675a9bd1a9213a1aeacd03f1dfa2c7","tid":1835724,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"人地城都封撚埋先出黎做下樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c9fa156befa38156d444683122a6bbc4aede67","tid":1835724,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:54:38.000Z","msg":"係武漢封撚咗站你先停，唔好再遲